@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. Mengecek Status Koneksi API & Database
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### 2. Registrasi Customer Baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Eko Prasetyo",
  "email": "eko@email.com",
  "password": "eko123"
}

### 3. Login Admin (Gunakan Response Token di Request Selanjutnya)
# Salin nilai token dari respon di bawah dan masukkan ke variabel @token di baris 26
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@toko.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Token JWT (Ganti token di bawah dengan token hasil Login di atas)
@token = token_jwt_hasil_login_di_sini

### 4. Ambil Semua Produk (Mendukung Pencarian/Filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?q=&category=&minPrice=&maxPrice=

### 5. Detail Satu Produk berdasarkan Kode
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/prod_001

### 6. Tambah Produk Baru (Memerlukan Akses Admin/Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_code": "prod_009",
  "name": "Topi Baseball Sport",
  "price": 85000,
  "category": "Pakaian",
  "description": "Topi baseball sport stylish dengan bahan katun drill berkualitas.",
  "image": "images/products/prod_009.jpg",
  "stock": 15
}

### 7. Proses Checkout Pesanan & Integrasi WhatsApp
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso",
  "phone": "08123456789",
  "address": "Jl. Merdeka No. 10, Jakarta Pusat",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "prod_001",
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": "prod_004",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 8. Ambil Riwayat Pesanan (Memerlukan Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Ubah Status Pesanan (Ganti ID Transaksi di URL dengan ID Transaksi Nyata)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/TXN-1719999999999-1234/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "paid"
}

### 10. Laporan Statistik Pelanggan (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Grafik Omzet Penjualan Kategori (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports/category-sales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
